 <PERSON> Bryan </PERSON> <PERSON> Brumley </PERSON>, a Washington-based national security reporter for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>, has been covering U.S.-Soviet affairs since 1981, when he was a correspondent in <LOCATION> Moscow </LOCATION>.
