<HEAD>Noriega Says U.S. Ultimatum Forced Collapse In Talks On His
Removal</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto NY4</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JOSEPH B. FRAZIER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>PANAMA CITY, Panama (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
