<HEAD>Iran-Contra Prosecution Hits Unprecedented Tangle</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto WX6</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By LARRY MARGASAK</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
