<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Ed </PERSON> <PERSON> Blanche </PERSON> is the <LOCATION> Middle </LOCATION> <LOCATION> East </LOCATION> news editor for The <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>. He has covered the gulf war since 1985.
