<HEAD>LaserPhoto upcoming</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By LISA PERLMAN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>ROCKFORD, Mich. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
